    public class LoadflowAlgorithmImpl
extends NetworkRefImpl<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>
implements LoadflowAlgorithm
    An implementation of the model object 'ILoadflow Algorithm'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Lf Method
    • Non Divergent
    • Max Iterations
    • Tolerance
    • Turn Off Island Bus
    • B11 Matrix Dirty
    • Gs Acc Factor
    • Init Bus Voltage
    • Data Check Config
    • Net Adj Algo
    • Lf Adj Algo
    • Custom Method
